  "timeline": [
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_001",
      "segment_index": 1,
      "narration_text": "我最近搭了一个 AI 短视频复盘系统。\n但它真正有用的地方，不是帮我做一张数据表。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_001.wav",
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 6.24,
      "duration": 6.24,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_002",
      "segment_index": 2,
      "narration_text": "而是每条视频发完以后，它能逼我回答一个问题：\n下一条，到底只改哪里？",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_002.wav",
      "start": 6.44,
      "end": 11.64,
      "duration": 5.2,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_003",
      "segment_index": 3,
      "narration_text": "以前我看数据，很容易乱。\n播放低，就怀疑选题。点赞少，就怀疑表达。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_003.wav",
      "start": 11.92,
      "end": 17.76,
      "duration": 5.84,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_004",
      "segment_index": 4,
      "narration_text": "没人私信，就怀疑方向。\n但这样其实没用。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_004.wav",
      "start": 17.96,
      "end": 20.92,
      "duration": 2.96,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_005",
      "segment_index": 5,
      "narration_text": "因为你每次都改一堆东西，下一条好了或者坏了，\n你也不知道到底是哪一步起作用。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_005.wav",
      "start": 21.12,
      "end": 26.0,
      "duration": 4.88,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_006",
      "segment_index": 6,
      "narration_text": "所以我没有让 AI 直接给我一个复盘结论。\n我先让它把这个复盘系统拆开。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_006.wav",
      "start": 26.2,
      "end": 31.4,
      "duration": 5.2,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_007",
      "segment_index": 7,
      "narration_text": "第一步，是配置。\n你做什么平台，账号目标是什么，看 24 小时、72 小时，还是 7 天数据，",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_007.wav",
      "start": 31.6,
      "end": 39.12,
      "duration": 7.52,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_008",
      "segment_index": 8,
      "narration_text": "哪些指标算观察信号，这些先写成可以改的配置。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_008.wav",
      "start": 39.32,
      "end": 43.4,
      "duration": 4.08,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_009",
      "segment_index": 9,
      "narration_text": "第二步，是字段。\n一条视频发完以后，不是只记播放量。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_009.wav",
      "start": 43.6,
      "end": 49.04,
      "duration": 5.44,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_010",
      "segment_index": 10,
      "narration_text": "它要分开记：2 秒跳出，5 秒完播，平均观看，收藏，评论，主页访问，私信，有效咨询。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_010.wav",
      "start": 49.24,
      "end": 57.24,
      "duration": 8.0,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_011",
      "segment_index": 11,
      "narration_text": "第三步，是截图入库。\n现在我每次发完视频，不是自己重新开表格慢慢填。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_011.wav",
      "start": 57.52,
      "end": 63.92,
      "duration": 6.4,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_012",
      "segment_index": 12,
      "narration_text": "我直接把后台截图丢给这个系统。\n它会先判断这是哪条视频，是 24 小时、72 小时，还是 7 天数据。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_012.wav",
      "start": 64.12,
      "end": 71.88,
      "duration": 7.76,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_013",
      "segment_index": 13,
      "narration_text": "然后把截图里的播放、跳出、完播、收藏、评论这些字段整理出来。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_013.wav",
      "start": 72.08,
      "end": 77.04,
      "duration": 4.96,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_014",
      "segment_index": 14,
      "narration_text": "看不见的字段，它不会乱猜，会直接标成缺失。\n看不准的地方，也会标成待确认。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_014.wav",
      "start": 77.24,
      "end": 83.24,
      "duration": 6.0,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_015",
      "segment_index": 15,
      "narration_text": "这样我拿到的就不是一堆截图，而是一份可以复盘的记录。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_015.wav",
      "start": 83.44,
      "end": 87.36,
      "duration": 3.92,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_016",
      "segment_index": 16,
      "narration_text": "第四步，是文案记录。\n每条视频原始文案要单独存下来。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_016.wav",
      "start": 87.56,
      "end": 91.96,
      "duration": 4.4,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_017",
      "segment_index": 17,
      "narration_text": "不能今天改一版，明天又改一版，\n最后连当时发出去的原文是什么都找不到。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_017.wav",
      "start": 92.16,
      "end": 97.28,
      "duration": 5.12,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_018",
      "segment_index": 18,
      "narration_text": "第五步，是问题层判断。\n数据不好，不能直接说这条废了。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_018.wav",
      "start": 97.48,
      "end": 103.0,
      "duration": 5.52,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_019",
      "segment_index": 19,
      "narration_text": "它要先判断问题出在哪一层：\n是标题封面没接住，是开头 5 秒没讲清，",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_019.wav",
      "start": 103.2,
      "end": 109.92,
      "duration": 6.72,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_020",
      "segment_index": 20,
      "narration_text": "是中段证据不够，是结尾没有承接动作，\n还是平台风险让内容被误伤。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_020.wav",
      "start": 110.2,
      "end": 115.88,
      "duration": 5.68,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_021",
      "segment_index": 21,
      "narration_text": "第六步，是下一轮变量。\n它最后不能给我十几个建议。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_021.wav",
      "start": 116.08,
      "end": 120.48,
      "duration": 4.4,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_022",
      "segment_index": 22,
      "narration_text": "它只应该收成一句话：\n下一条先改哪个变量，改完看哪个指标。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_022.wav",
      "start": 120.68,
      "end": 125.4,
      "duration": 4.72,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_023",
      "segment_index": 23,
      "narration_text": "比如改开头，就看 2 秒跳出、3 秒留存、5 秒完播。\n改中段，就看平均观看和完播。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_023.wav",
      "start": 125.68,
      "end": 133.28,
      "duration": 7.6,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_024",
      "segment_index": 24,
      "narration_text": "改承接，就看收藏、评论、主页访问和私信。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_024.wav",
      "start": 133.48,
      "end": 138.84,
      "duration": 5.36,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_025",
      "segment_index": 25,
      "narration_text": "这个系统现在还不是最终版。\n但它已经解决了我以前最大的问题：",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_025.wav",
      "start": 139.04,
      "end": 143.04,
      "duration": 4.0,
      "pause_after": 0.28
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_026",
      "segment_index": 26,
      "narration_text": "我不是凭感觉做下一条了。\n每条视频发完，至少能留下一个可复盘、可修改、可验证的动作。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_026.wav",
      "start": 143.32,
      "end": 150.28,
      "duration": 6.96,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_027",
      "segment_index": 27,
      "narration_text": "如果你也想做自己的短视频复盘系统，\n我把我这套整理成了通用版。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_027.wav",
      "start": 150.48,
      "end": 155.76,
      "duration": 5.28,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_028",
      "segment_index": 28,
      "narration_text": "不是固定模板，而是一套可以改的提示词结构。\n你可以把自己的平台、账号目标、视频类型和指标填进去，",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_028.wav",
      "start": 155.96,
      "end": 165.0,
      "duration": 9.04,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_029",
      "segment_index": 29,
      "narration_text": "再交给 Trae 这类 AI 编程工具，\n先搭出一版自己的复盘系统。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_029.wav",
      "start": 165.2,
      "end": 169.76,
      "duration": 4.56,
      "pause_after": 0.2
    },
    {
      "line_group_id": "lg_030",
      "segment_index": 30,
      "narration_text": "不是保证爆款。\n是先让你别再凭感觉乱改。",
      "audio_path": "dist/fourth_episode_ai_review_system_publish_candidate/tts_segments/seg_030.wav",
      "start": 169.96,
      "end": 173.88,
      "duration": 3.92,
